21
00:00:50,567 --> 00:00:54,791
Sunday, 1pm at the open area
at "Ebisu Garden Place" near the clock.

22
00:00:54,791 --> 00:01:00,064
And this irritating guy actually
did something as outrageous as...

23
00:01:00,064 --> 00:01:01,617
Unbelievable.

24
00:01:02,142 --> 00:01:03,560
Why?

25
00:01:18,975 --> 00:01:20,982
Um..

26
00:01:24,956 --> 00:01:26,250
Makino!

27
00:01:30,112 --> 00:01:32,146
C... C... Cold...

28
00:01:43,687 --> 00:01:45,770
W... Wait a minute.

29
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:50,840
Suddenly grabbing me like that.
What on earth are you trying to do?

30
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:53,071
I'm glad that you're safe.

31
00:01:53,568 --> 00:01:54,639
Eh?

32
00:01:55,095 --> 00:01:58,413
I was afraid you might be in trouble.

33
00:01:58,413 --> 00:02:00,518
