I never even agreed to you in the first place.

38
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,455
Didn't I ask you?

39
00:02:13,455 --> 00:02:14,262
Eh?

40
00:02:14,262 --> 00:02:17,955
You were actually here long before already.

41
00:02:19,766 --> 00:02:23,576
Perhaps, you've fallen for me?

42
00:02:25,348 --> 00:02:26,936
Huh?

43
00:02:30,321 --> 00:02:31,313
Wait... Wait...

44
00:02:42,970 --> 00:02:46,131
This can't be good.
It's so cold.

45
00:02:54,881 --> 00:02:58,047
Let's go and have some hot tea.

46
00:02:58,958 --> 00:03:00,613
You really make people angry.

47
00:03:04,413 --> 00:03:06,018
Let's go then.

48
00:03:06,487 --> 00:03:10,606
Huh? Wait for me.

49
00:03:21,575 --> 00:03:22,970
Wait a minute.

50
00:03:32,925 --> 00:03:34,033
Let's stop here.

51
00:03:34,033 --> 00:03:35,291
This building is 4 storeys high.

52
00:03:35,291 --> 00:03:37,477
The Ebisu sold here is delicious and cheap.

53
00:03:37,477 --> 00:03:38,569
They even sell cake here.

54
00:03:38,569 --> 00:03:40,190
Are you sure, here?

55
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:42,472
Do you come here often?

56
00:03:42,472 --> 00:03:44,051
Don't complain so much.

57
00:03:44,051 --> 00:03:45,690
I don't like it.

58
00:03:45,690 --> 00:03:47,284
Eating at low-class places like these,

59
00:03:47,284 --> 00:03:49,366
my pride doesn't permit it.

60
00:03:49,366 --> 00:03:53,155
"Doesn't permit it"?
Don't you think that you shouldn't always be
so concerned about your pride?

61
00:03:53,155 --> 00:03:54,377
Hi there Miss.

62
00:03:54,377 --> 00:03:56,896
Please take a look. We are doing a survey.

63
00:03:56,896 --> 00:03:59,120
Please look carefully.

64
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,334
That...

65
00:04:00,334 --> 00:04:01,987
