76
00:04:29,291 --> 00:04:30,555
"Bello"...?

77
00:04:30,555 --> 00:04:32,533
Could your Japanese be quite weak?

78
00:04:32,533 --> 00:04:35,598
Does it matter if my Japanese is weak?
It's just that I'm not good with words.

79
00:04:35,598 --> 00:04:37,036
He really is dumb.

80
00:04:42,613 --> 00:04:45,751
Eh? It's not working.

81
00:04:45,751 --> 00:04:47,004
Hey hey hey.

82
00:04:47,004 --> 00:04:48,780
Don't tell me its spoilt.

83
00:04:54,431 --> 00:04:55,834
It can't be...

84
00:04:55,834 --> 00:04:57,108
You're joking.

85
00:04:57,108 --> 00:04:59,107
Hey hey!

86
00:04:59,107 --> 00:05:00,978
Anyone out there?

87
00:05:04,042 --> 00:05:05,445
It can't be.

88
00:05:05,445 --> 00:05:06,954
Let's call for help.

89
