123
00:06:57,034 --> 00:06:59,509
Disgusting.

124
00:07:07,705 --> 00:07:11,205
Help!!

125
00:07:14,574 --> 00:07:16,498
What on earth are you doing?

126
00:07:16,988 --> 00:07:19,426
It's so scary. So scary...

127
00:07:19,974 --> 00:07:20,851
Grab this.

128
00:07:20,851 --> 00:07:22,755
