129
00:07:22,755 --> 00:07:23,939
Stupid,

130
00:07:23,939 --> 00:07:25,594
now's not the time to be saying such things.

131
00:07:25,594 --> 00:07:28,107
I'm... I'm scared.

132
00:07:28,107 --> 00:07:29,823
Help me quickly!

133
00:07:29,823 --> 00:07:30,882
Here...

134
00:07:58,028 --> 00:07:59,200
Makino...

135
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,332
Huh?

136
00:08:04,154 --> 00:08:05,137
What?

137
00:08:10,433 --> 00:08:11,367
St... Stop.

138
00:08:11,367 --> 00:08:14,044
I'll never forgive you if you do something perverted.

139
00:08:16,496 --> 00:08:17,689
I...

140
