153
00:08:56,836 --> 00:09:01,150
It refers to a situation which is extremely dangerous,
that's "Kikiippatsu".

154
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,514
I see.

155
00:09:02,514 --> 00:09:06,572
Listen here, kid. Don't write the word wrongly as "hand".
("Kiki" for "te")

156
00:09:06,572 --> 00:09:09,027
"Kikiipatsu"!!

157
00:09:11,205 --> 00:09:14,996
Please don't say such lame things, dad.
You really are very childish.

158
00:09:15,211 --> 00:09:18,574
Yea... Well then dad will only drink 
a bottle of beer only next week.

159
00:09:18,574 --> 00:09:21,392
