188
00:13:16,211 --> 00:13:17,693
Sorry.

189
00:13:20,507 --> 00:13:22,272
Then again,

190
00:13:22,272 --> 00:13:26,572
we ended up like this
because you were late in the first place.

191
00:13:30,470 --> 00:13:31,629
What's so funny?

192
00:13:31,629 --> 00:13:37,715
In this state, you no longer have the dignity
of a member of F4.

193
00:13:39,191 --> 00:13:40,520
Shush.

194
00:13:47,262 --> 00:13:49,048
The Red Paper...

195
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:53,010
I revoked it.

196
00:13:54,668 --> 00:13:59,241
Perhaps it's a bit too late.

197
00:14:02,886 --> 00:14:05,058
You're only kidding yourself.

198
00:14:07,558 --> 00:14:10,860
