You can't just enter the building before it opens.

205
00:16:16,758 --> 00:16:20,487
If you want to do those sort of things, go to a hotel.

206
00:16:27,032 --> 00:16:29,571
Can you make it back alone?

207
00:16:29,924 --> 00:16:31,423
Yea.

208
00:16:32,077 --> 00:16:33,892
Makino. About that...

209
00:16:33,892 --> 00:16:38,904
I'm really sorry for the mess I made.

210
00:16:40,339 --> 00:16:42,284
Then let me thank you...


211
00:16:42,284 --> 00:16:43,762
Eh?

212
00:16:45,834 --> 00:16:47,826
Quickly apologise...

213
00:16:49,213 --> 00:16:50,944
Apologise...?

214
00:16:57,023 --> 00:16:58,599
Stop!

215
00:16:58,599 --> 00:17:03,239
Did the two of you kiss then?

216
00:17:03,239 --> 00:17:05,294
How could we?

217
00:17:05,294 --> 00:17:08,325
I never intended to.
I ran before he could do anything.

218
00:17:08,325 --> 00:17:09,538
Oh.

219
00:17:10,243 --> 00:17:13,729
So, your family must be quite worried.

220
00:17:16,334 --> 00:17:17,703
Oh no, they're the worst...

221
00:17:17,703 --> 00:17:20,741
You never even came to us to discuss
what you wanted to do!

222
00:17:21,693 --> 00:17:23,340
I'm sorry.

223
00:17:25,150 --> 00:17:32,831
I never thought that onee-chan would resort
to doing those sort of things.

224
00:17:34,012 --> 00:17:35,909
I'm sorry.

225
00:17:38,410 --> 00:17:39,715
Where exactly did you go?

226
00:17:39,715 --> 00:17:45,352
Dad thought you met with great trouble.

227
00:17:48,505 --> 00:17:52,079
This is the result of spending the night away from home
for the very first time.

228
00:17:52,088 --> 00:17:54,658
You didn't have any problems in school?

229
00:17:54,658 --> 00:17:58,634
