Tsuki...

235
00:18:17,419 --> 00:18:29,267
Tsuki... Tsuki... Tsuki.........

236
00:18:29,728 --> 00:18:31,866
Tsuki...?

237
00:18:34,254 --> 00:18:36,075
Not bad eh, Tsuki.

238
00:18:37,691 --> 00:18:39,447
I'm really envious.

239
00:18:42,586 --> 00:18:47,046
