They're here.

246
00:19:21,331 --> 00:19:22,553
Yo!

247
00:19:28,822 --> 00:19:31,515
Hey Tsukasa. Is this true?

248
00:19:31,515 --> 00:19:32,418
No... That's...

249
00:19:32,418 --> 00:19:33,945
Ah, it's true.

250
00:19:33,945 --> 00:19:34,527
Eh?

251
00:19:36,586 --> 00:19:40,053
Hey hey. Seems like Tsukasa has become more of a man.

252
00:19:40,053 --> 00:19:41,045
I guess.

253
00:19:41,045 --> 00:19:42,556
Wait a minute...

254
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:51,240
Perhaps Doumyoji-san really likes you?

255
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:53,123
No way that can happen.

256
00:19:54,067 --> 00:20:01,037
